<p>party, but Gray &amp; I, on ahead, went one way &amp; they another.  All arrived about same time, &amp; found 3rd bearers with the 2nd.<br/>3rd Amb <strike>dest</strike> whereabouts unknown<br/>Riot with Portuguese in evening<br/>Billets in a barn.<br/>Coffee at estament with Eva &amp; Clough.  Gray found brother.<br/>Commenced this morning to continue march to rest camp.  Arrived Halte D'ouve, soon after dinner.  On main road to Boulogne.<br/>Reunion of old pals with me, (who have been with 2nd some time).</p>
